Useful rake tasks for:
	- dumping a mysql database (take a snapshot)
	- importing a mysql databse (and running migrations)
	- loading bootstrap data from a folder full of yml's or csv's
	- using an snapshop db file (migrated) for running specs on (RSPEC)

